flowchart TD
    A[Broker 启动] --> B{abort 文件存在?}
    B -->|否| N[正常恢复]
    B -->|是| X[异常恢复]
    N --> C[加载并恢复 ConsumeQueue/Index]
    X --> C
    C --> D[计算各派生存储最小 dispatchFromPhyOffset]
    D --> E{恢复模式}
    E -->|正常| F[CommitLog#recoverNormally〔R5.5〕]
    E -->|异常| G[CommitLog#recoverAbnormally〔R5.5〕]
    F --> H[逐条校验 TotalSize/Magic/长度/可选 CRC]
    G --> H
    H --> I{完整合法记录?}
    I -->|是| J[推进 processOffset<br/>必要时重建 CQ/Index]
    J --> H
    I -->|BLANK| K[切到下一文件]
    I -->|半条/非法/CRC错| L[停止扫描]
    K --> H
    L --> M[截断 CommitLog 脏尾]
    M --> O[截断超前 CQ/Index<br/>设置 wrote/commit/flush 水位]
    O --> P[恢复 topicQueueTable 并启动分发]
